src/web/manager.description: Main frontend directory containing 48+ React components, 4 custom hooks, services, contexts, and types. Components are organized into ui/, layout/, chat/ subdirectories.

src/web/manager/components/ui.description: UI primitive components directory with 11 reusable components: Button, Input, Select, Textarea, Switch, Card, Dialog, ProgressBar, ArrayEditor, KeyValueEditor, Icons

src/web/manager/hooks.description: Custom hooks directory with 4 hooks: useAgentCreator (agent creation with SSE), useAssistantRuntime (runtime management), useSkillCreator (skill creation), useSkillTraining (training workflow)
